title: Two Whats?! And A Wow! - Part Animal, All Wow (9/30/22)
description:
What do koalas and Mindy have in common? And why are Mindy and Guy Raz comparing themselves to animals anyway?! We've got the questions AND answers in this paw-some round of Two Whats?! And A Wow! We're challenging you to find the facts from the fiction about animal similarities! Originally aired 10/8/21.
